Plan: Accelerating Givoro User Growth with Optimized Caching and Multi-Affiliate Integration

Based on your priorities (user growth, in-memory caching optimization, and Etsy/ClickBank/Nike affiliates), this plan focuses on maximizing user acquisition and retention while expanding revenue channels without requiring external services like Redis.

1. Core User Growth Infrastructure (Week 1-2)

Implement "Save for Later" functionality with localStorage persistence and heart icons on all gift cards
Create "My Saved Gifts" page accessible from header navigation for returning users
Build email capture modal that triggers after 3+ saves to enable cross-device sync
Add social sharing buttons on each gift card with WhatsApp, Facebook, Twitter, and copy link functionality
Create shareable URLs that generate public gift detail pages for viral distribution
Implement referral tracking in shareable links to measure organic growth channels
2. Advanced In-Memory Caching System (Week 1-2)

Build intelligent TTL-based cache system with configurable expiration per cache type
Implement LRU eviction strategy to prevent memory overflow with max size limits
Create cache warming on application startup for top 50 most popular queries
Add cache hit rate tracking and performance metrics dashboard endpoint
Implement predictive cache pre-loading based on user conversation state patterns
Build cache persistence to Bolt Database for cross-instance warm cache restoration
Add request deduplication with in-flight request tracking to prevent duplicate API calls
3. SEO and Organic Traffic Growth (Week 2-3)

Create 20 SEO-optimized static gift guide pages targeting high-volume search terms
Implement server-side rendering for gift guide pages with proper meta tags and schema markup
Build automated sitemap generation with gift guide page indexing
Add Open Graph tags for rich social media previews on shared links
Create blog section with gift advice content linking to main recommendation flow
Implement breadcrumb navigation and internal linking structure for SEO
4. Multi-Affiliate Integration Framework (Week 3-4)

Design unified affiliate provider interface for consistent product data structure
Build Etsy affiliate integration with API authentication and product search
Implement ClickBank marketplace integration with category mapping
Add Nike affiliate program integration via their partner API
Create retailer badge system showing product source on gift cards
Implement smart retailer selection based on product category and availability
Build conversion tracking by retailer to optimize future product selection
5. Product Discovery and Comparison (Week 3-4)

Create product comparison feature with checkbox selection on gift cards
Build floating comparison bar that appears when 2-3 products are selected
Implement side-by-side comparison modal with price, features, and ratings
Add "Show Similar" button on each gift card for alternative product discovery
Build expanded product view showing 3-5 related items in same category
Implement price range filtering within similar products section
6. Personalization and User Retention (Week 4-5)

Build gift personality profiling quiz with 5 questions about recipient preferences
Create user profile system storing quiz results and recommendation history
Implement "Refine Results" feature allowing criteria adjustment without restart
Add contextual follow-up questions after initial suggestions for better targeting
Build negative filtering multi-select to exclude unwanted gift categories
Store user preferences in Bolt Database linked to email for cross-device personalization
7. Conversion Optimization (Week 5-6)

Implement dynamic commission optimization prioritizing high-commission products
Add "Why This Gift?" expandable modal with detailed AI reasoning and visual icons
Create "Complete the Gift" upsell modal showing gift wrap and card options
Build progressive disclosure pattern for product details to reduce cognitive load
Add trust signals including review counts, Amazon ratings, and delivery timeframes
Implement exit-intent popup capturing email before abandonment
8. Analytics and Growth Measurement (Week 6)

Build comprehensive admin analytics dashboard with user growth metrics
Add funnel visualization showing drop-off points in conversation flow
Implement cohort analysis tracking retention rates by acquisition channel
Create A/B testing framework for testing UI variations and prompt changes
Build conversion attribution tracking by traffic source and affiliate partner
Add export functionality for all analytics data to CSV format
