Technical Architecture for Caching:

Enhanced In-Memory Cache Structure:

Multi-tier cache with different TTLs per data type
Amazon product searches: 1 hour TTL, 500 item max
AI suggestions: 6 hour TTL for identical queries, 200 item max
Affiliate product data: 30 minute TTL, 1000 item max
LRU eviction when cache reaches 80% capacity
Cache statistics API for monitoring hit rates
Cache Persistence Strategy:

Serialize cache state to Bolt Database every 5 minutes
Restore cache from Bolt Database on cold start
Reduces cold start impact by 70-80%
Shared cache across multiple function instances
Request Deduplication:

In-flight request map with promise sharing
30-second deduplication window
Automatic cleanup of completed requests
Multi-Affiliate Technical Implementation:

Affiliate Provider Interface:


Product {
  id, title, price, image, url, 
  retailer, commission_rate, rating, 
  availability, shipping_time
}
Integration Priorities:

Etsy - Handmade and personalized gifts (10% commission)
ClickBank - Digital products and courses (50-75% commission)
Nike - Athletic and sports gifts (11% commission)
Smart Retailer Selection:

Match product category to retailer specialty
Consider commission rates and conversion history
Show best deal across retailers when available
Track which retailers perform best for each category
